abstract: Federal Judge Mark Walker rejects motion by Florida State to dismiss former student Erica Kinsman's lawsuit charging that university did not properly investigate her rape claims against football star Jameis Winston.
lead_paragraph: A United States district judge denied Florida State’s motion to dismiss a lawsuit filed by the former student Erica Kinsman, who has said Jameis Winston sexually assaulted her in 2012.

headline.main: Judge Denies Motion to Dismiss F.S.U. Suit
headline.print_headline: Judge Denies Motion to Dismiss Suit
